   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Our father it is who writes to his sons, the brothers of the poll tax, that, in the matter of the solidus for the poll tax, which Chimoul is obliged to pay for this year, the eleventh indiction, a solidus worth of carpenting has come to me for it. Phamenoth 17, indiction 11. Phiph.;(2nd hd.) Kyros."</ab>
         </div>
